Gloria Hunniford, Angela Rippon and Julia Somerville investigate the truth 
about the foods we eat, from the secrets of the supermarkets to the reality of 
what's behind the labels.

The team meet a woman who thinks nothing of eating the decades-old ingredients 
lurking at the back of her kitchen cupboard - so which are still safe to eat?
